1781979632158602	paintop-dev	itc:v3:AWKTkkmcyckyeZEAAAAAQa6q3a6te0AAAAEzwAI		item.create	bn-347	{"description":"Update notes/paintop-plan so the implementation plan no longer tells workers to build the deferred SDF chain for the first vertical slice. Specifically: rewrite plan.md §25 steps 3-4 to use a soft-edged ellipse mask with analytic feather by physical pixel radius; rewrite docs/IR_SPEC.md §20 to remove mask.to_sdf / sdf.to_mask / allowed-mask nodes and use mask.ellipse@1 with edge { profile: smoothstep, half_width_px: N } plus composite.masked_replace@1 as the single authorization boundary; add the OP_CATALOG §4 note from M0_DECISIONS.md D1 that exact EDT + SDF is M1.5 priority immediately after the loop is green. Acceptance: rg over the north-star/MVP example shows no SDF dependency in the M0/MVP path, while M1.5 still owns exact EDT/SDF work.","kind":"task","labels":["planning","group-conformance"],"parent":"bn-6pu","size":"s","title":"Align planning docs with non-SDF MVP touch-up loop"}	blake3:jL7pZeKWLLSbOFubAoaiwkxHZyCDkogyPxanmmp2gww
