1781979701998846	paintop-dev	itc:v3:AWKTkkmcyckyeZEAAAAAQa6q3a6te0AAAAEzxgI		item.create	bn-we1	{"description":"Add the initial fuzz harness expected by plan.md §19 M0 and AGENT_VERIFICATION quality goals. Scope: introduce a standard Rust fuzz setup (cargo-fuzz/libFuzzer or the repo-approved equivalent) without making it part of every local ; add seed corpus directories and two first targets: (1) strict plan parsing/canonicalization rejects malformed JSON, duplicate-key-like structures, invalid numbers, excessive nesting/size, and unknown fields without panics or unbounded allocation; (2) PNG decode/encode boundary fuzzing exercises malformed/truncated/oversized inputs through the hardened decode limits without panics. Acceptance: fuzz targets build in CI/nightly or an explicit  job, smoke-run for a bounded time, and any crash artifact is captured under target/fuzz/artifacts with reproduction instructions. References: plan.md §17.2, §19 M0; AGENT_VERIFICATION §2.1/§2.2.","kind":"task","labels":["group-conformance","quality"],"parent":"bn-6pu","size":"m","title":"Fuzz scaffolding for plan parser and image codec boundaries"}	blake3:NJmnE0exoJbRoQRJlRFHfqRr0Wb_vO9hhkAug5N1dP4
